<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About us</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      data-purpose="Layout StyleSheet"
      title="Web Awesome"
      href="/css/app-wa-462d1fe84b879d730fe2180b0e0354e0.css?vsn=d"
    />

    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://site-assets.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.5.1/css/all.css"
    />

    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://site-assets.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.5.1/css/sharp-thin.css"
    />

    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://site-assets.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.5.1/css/sharp-solid.css"
    />

    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://site-assets.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.5.1/css/sharp-regular.css"
    />

    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://site-assets.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.5.1/css/sharp-light.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/about.css" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="overflow-x-hidden">
    <%- include("../partials/header.ejs") %>
    <main>
      <section id="section" class="flex items-center justify-center flex-col">
        <div id="top" class="flex items-center justify-center p-3 gap-12">
          <img
            src="./images/jobs.jpg"
            alt=""
            class="w-[800px] h-[500px]"
            id="job"
          />
          <div
            id="about"
            class="gap-3 flex items-center justify-center flex-col w-[480px]"
          >
            <h1 class="text-[50px] font-bold text-center text-[#1f4a79]">
              About ProCareer
            </h1>
            <p class="text-[16px] text-[#414141] text-justify">
              Welcome to
              <span class="font-bold text-blue-500">ProCareer</span>, your
              one-stop platform for all things related to job searching and
              career development. Our mission is to empower individuals to reach
              their full potential by connecting them with the right
              opportunities, resources, and tools to build a successful career.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[16px] text-[#414141] text-justify">
              At ProCareer, we understand that finding the right job is more
              than just matching skills to roles; it's about aligning your
              career aspirations with opportunities that truly resonate with
              you. That is why we have built a platform that not only helps you
              discover job openings but also supports your continuous growth
              through personalized career development resources.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div
            id="bottom"
            class="flex items-center justify-center flex-col px-10"
          >
            <div
              id="bottom-content"
              class="bg-white rounded-lg p-10 gap-4 flex items-center justify-center flex-col text-justify"
            >
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[#1f4a79]">Our Vision</h2>
              <p class="text-[16px] text-[#414141]">
                We envision a world where everyone has access to meaningful work
                that aligns with their passions and strengths. Through
                ProCareer, we strive to bridge the gap between job seekers and
                employers by offering an intuitive, user-friendly platform that
                simplifies the job search process and enhances career growth.
              </p>

              <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[#1f4a79]">Our Mission</h2>
              <ul class="text-[#414141] flex items-center justify-evenly gap-3">
                <li class="text-[16px] p-3">
                  <span class="font-bold text-blue-500">Connect:</span> Bridge
                  the gap between talent and opportunities by providing a
                  platform where job seekers can find roles that fit their
                  skills and career goals.
                </li>
                <li class="text-[16px] p-3">
                  <span class="font-bold text-blue-500">Empower:</span> Offer
                  personalized career development resources, including courses,
                  workshops, and mentorship, to help users grow professionally.
                </li>
                <li class="text-[16px] p-3">
                  <span class="font-bold text-blue-500">Support:</span> Create a
                  community where individuals can share insights, seek advice,
                  and collaborate to advance their careers.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[#1f4a79]">
                Why Choose ProCareer?
              </h2>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                <li class="text-[16px] text-[#414141]">
                  <span class="font-bold text-blue-500"
                    >Tailored Job Matches:</span
                  >
                  Our advanced algorithms ensure that you receive job
                  recommendations that are aligned with your skills, experience,
                  and career goals.
                </li>
                <li class="text-[16px] text-[#414141]">
                  <span class="font-bold text-blue-500"
                    >Career Development Tools:</span
                  >
                  From resume building to interview preparation, ProCareer
                  offers a wide range of tools designed to help you succeed in
                  your career journey.
                </li>
                <li class="text-[16px] text-[#414141]">
                  <span class="font-bold text-blue-500"
                    >Continuous Learning:</span
                  >
                  Stay ahead of the curve with access to industry-specific
                  courses and certifications that enhance your skill set.
                </li>
                <li class="text-[16px] text-[#414141]">
                  <span class="font-bold text-blue-500"
                    >Community Support:</span
                  >
                  Connect with like-minded professionals, mentors, and industry
                  experts to gain insights and advice on navigating your career
                  path.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <p class="text-[16px] text-[#414141]">
                Join
                <span class="font-bold text-blue-500">ProCareer</span> today and
                take the next step towards achieving your career goals. Whether
                you're just starting out or looking to advance in your field,
                we're here to support you every step of the way.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <%- include("../partials/footer.ejs") %>
  </body>
</html>
